    {
      "id": "m5699e59024044ff9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 135,
      "width": 305.65999999999997,
      "height": 22.950000000000003,
      "text": "❌ Prompt Direto com PRD Gigante",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "angle": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roughness": 0,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": null,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "locked": false,
      "seed": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "updated": 1,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid"
    },
    {
      "id": "ma9057781dcfd49c2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 168,
      "width": 243.6,
      "height": 324.0,
      "text": "O que acontece:\n• A IA prioriza o início\n• Ignora o meio\n• Alucina no final\n\nÉ o mesmo problema da janela\nde contexto cheia, aplicado ao\ndesenvolvimento de software.\n\n50 requisitos num prompt só →\nresultado raso e incoerente.\n\nAnalogia:\nPedir pra um dev implementar 50\nfeatures sem dividir em tasks,\nsem critério de aceite, sem\ndefinição de pronto.\n\nResultado: frustração, retrabalho,\n\"IA não presta pra projeto grande\".",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "angle": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roughness": 0,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": null,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "locked": false,
      "seed": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "updated": 1,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid"
    },
    {
      "id": "m4a5308b251e94234",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 510,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 430,
      "height": 450,
      "backgroundColor": "#f0fff4",
      "strokeColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "angle": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roughness": 0,
