    {
      "id": "mc6bee03f3dcf456a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1150,
      "y": 895,
      "width": 178.64,
      "height": 103.95,
      "text": "Abrir o leque — pesquisar\nabordagens, bibliotecas,\npatterns. Fase exploratória.\n\nPergunte: \"Quais as opções?\nO que a comunidade usa?\nQuais os trade-offs?\"",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "angle": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roughness": 0,
      "roundness": null,
