    },
    {
      "id": "mc4a443e0b8b54577",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1160,
      "y": 1202,
      "width": 919.8799999999999,
      "height": 17.55,
      "text": "Evita o \"vibe coding\" — codar no feeling sem planejar. Cada decisão tem racional documentado que pode ser revisado depois.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "angle": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roughness": 0,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": null,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "locked": false,
      "seed": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "updated": 1,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid"
    },
    {
      "id": "m10a1a16d44674926",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1160,
      "y": 1230,
      "width": 897.26,
      "height": 17.55,
      "text": "RPI é o micro-ciclo dentro de cada fase. SDD é o macro-ciclo do projeto. Juntos = disciplina de desenvolvimento com IA.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "angle": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
